This is a sentence with a reference to a footnote attached to it.[NTE:one]

*	NTE:one
	Here is the content of that footnote, which should be displayed at
	the bottom of the page on which it is referenced, but may occur
	anywhere in the source document (modulo scope).

*	NTE:two
	This is a named footnote, which is only displayed in the compiled
	document if referenced, and otherwise acts as a comment.

If a footnote is referenced multiple times[NTE:times], it will be displayed
multiple times with the same content but different numbering.[NTE:one]


*	NTE:times
	Any number of times.
